{
  "info": {
    "name": "SecureApp API",
    "_postman_id": "secureapp-pps-2026",
    "description": "Colección completa de pruebas para SecureApp — Proyecto PPS\n\nCubre todos los endpoints de la API REST:\n- Autenticación (login, token JWT)\n- Proyectos (GET, POST)\n- Administración (usuarios, logs, stats)\n- Seguridad (rate limiting, autorización)\n\nVariables de entorno necesarias:\n- base_url: http://localhost:5000\n- admin_token: (se rellena automáticamente al hacer login)\n- user_token: (se rellena automáticamente al hacer login usuario)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "admin_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "project_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - Health Check",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/health — servicio OK",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('status es ok', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.status).to.eql('ok');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.service).to.eql('backend-api');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.database).to.exist;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.engine).to.eql('MySQL 8');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Content-Type es JSON', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get('Content-Type')).to.include('application/json');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/health",
            "description": "Comprueba que el backend y MySQL están funcionando"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - Autenticación",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/login — admin correcto ✅",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Devuelve token JWT', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.token).to.exist;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.token.split('.')).to.have.lengthOf(3);",
                  "    pm.expect(json.role).to.eql('admin');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.username).to.eql('admin');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.message).to.exist;",
                  "});",
                  "// Guardar token para siguientes requests",
                  "const token = pm.response.json().token;",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', token);",
                  "pm.test('Token guardado en variable', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('admin_token')).to.eql(token);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin1234!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/login",
            "description": "Login con credenciales de administrador. Guarda el token automáticamente."
